# AsFix Mobile & i18n

## Languages — exactly 3
- Supported: `en`, `roman`, `ur` only — defined in `frontend/src/locales/translations.js`
- Do not add world-languages picker or extra locale blocks (caused syntax breaks and hangs)
- All user-facing strings go through `t('key')` — add keys to all 3 locales when adding UI text
- Urdu mode sets `dir="rtl"` — test navbar, footer, forms in RTL

## Mobile performance
- Respect `mobile-performance.css`: no backdrop-blur on mobile, ambient bg off, scroll-behavior auto
- Menu thumb animation: use spring in `useNavDrawerThumb.js`; stop rAF when menu closed
- Avoid lazy routes that showed stuck "Load ho raha hai" — keep eager imports in `PageTransition.jsx` unless Suspense is tested
- Gaming/Shop mode transitions: keep navigate delay under ~700ms
- Poll APIs with `startVisibilityPoll` — pause when tab hidden

## Touch UX
- `(pointer: coarse)` — disable heavy hover/magnetic/ripple effects
- Keep floating buttons (`cart`, `WhatsApp`, `gaming`) from overlapping on small screens
- Test at 375px width and RTL before shipping UI changes
